c finite-cardinality-v0 no-injection-four-to-three
c Variables x_{i,j} mean domain element p_i maps to codomain element h_j.
c Variable number is 3*i + j + 1 for i in 0..3 and j in 0..2.
c Clauses require each p_i to map somewhere, each p_i to map to at most one h_j,
c and no two p_i values to share the same h_j. This is the 4-into-3 pigeonhole
c obstruction for injective total functions.
p cnf 12 34
